[About]

This will generate a headless ubuntu server precise64 '.box' ready to be used in virtualbox (by vagrant) and with chef as the provisioning tool 

[Installation]

assuming you are on a linux or mac environment:

install 
-virtualbox
-packer
-vagrant

clone this repository


[Usage]

run "create_box.sh"

It will create a box under "build" folder, after that you can run your vagrant file (you should create one) and point to 'precise64-rails-dev' box